# GoHighLevel Integration Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values

# GoHighLevel API Configuration
GHL_API_KEY=your-ghl-api-key-here
GHL_LOCATION_ID=your-location-id-here
GHL_WEBHOOK_URL=your-webhook-url-here

# Centerfy.ai Integration Configuration
CENTERFY_PROJECT_ID=your-centerfy-project-id-here
CENTERFY_API_KEY=your-centerfy-api-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Get your API key from GoHighLevel Settings > Integrations > API
# 2. Find your Location ID in GoHighLevel Settings > Company
# 3. Create a webhook URL in GoHighLevel Workflows > Triggers > Inbound Webhook
# 4. Get your Centerfy.ai credentials from https://centerfy.ai/dashboard
# 5. Replace the placeholder values above with your actual credentials
# 6. Rename this file to .env (remove .example)